            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1. Navigate to http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/demobrowser/#virtual~Tree.html

2. Drag the folder icon on the right side in white space.

3. Observe that &quot;New Item 0&quot; has been added under the root element.

4. Check &quot;Hide Root Node&quot;

5. Perform step 2 again

6. Observe that no New Item appears to have been added.

7. Uncheck &quot;Hide Root Node&quot;

8. Observe that &quot;New Item 1&quot; is now visible.</thetext>
